  "title": "Administrative Assistant ",
  "description": "<p>We are looking for a dynamic individual to join our team as an <u><strong>Administrative  Assistant</strong></u>.</p><p><u><strong>Responsibilities</strong></u></p><p><br /></p><p>· Provide Administrative support to our office (Quotations of Products, responding to queries emails, etc)</p><p>· Typing of product labels and relaying of orders from Business Clients to Kitchen. </p><p>· Preparation of ISO/HACCP and Halal Certification documents</p><p>· Purchasing of inventory/ Ingredients from suppliers</p><p>· Receiving of Goods and directing delivery man for storage of goods</p><p>· Process Delivery order/ Invoices (If needed)</p><p><br /></p><p><u><strong>Requirements</strong></u></p><p>· Good Organization skills and Attention to detail</p><p>· Independent Team player</p><p>· Able to commit to a 5 Days work week (9 am to 6 pm)</p><p>· Experienced/Non-experienced applicants are welcomed</p><p>· Proficient in Microsoft Office and Excel</p><p>· Excellent Verbal and Written communication skills (English)</p><p><br /></p><p><u><strong>Please send a complete resume to info@thecakefactory.com.sg including:</strong></u></p><p>· Personal details and contact information</p><p>· All relevant and past work experience with references.</p><p>· Last drawn salary or expected salary.</p><p>· Date of availability.</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</strong></p>",
